These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | onion   | orange   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
City: new-york, london
1. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
2. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice   |
| City      | london | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
